1st ==> go inside your file directory.
2nd ==> run in your terminal " npm install ", to install the required packages.
3rd ==> create a file in your main directory named " nodemon.json ".
4th ==> in your nodemon.json file create an object like so...
        {
          "env": {
            "MONGO_ATLAS_PW": "your mongo atlas or cluster password here",
            "MONGO_ATLAS_DB": "name of the DB in mongo"
          }
        }
        replace the values with your own credentials.